snippet.textDisplay: Looking forward to this!!! Have been listening to Coke Studio India and Pakistan before, but I think I can make an approximation and say, what we got was a prolific amount of north Indian music primarily in Coke Studio India, and not really as much from the other regions. As someone with the mothertongue of bengali, the lack of having more bengali songs (and the musical genres that of the said region too) was sorely felt for for me. As such, this project is absolutely a delight !

snippet.textDisplay: কোক  স্টুডিওকে বাংলাদেশে সুস্বাগতম।আশাকরি বাংলাদেশের আনাচে কানাচে প্রতিভাবান শিল্পীদের অসম্ভব সুন্দর বাংলা গান,লোকগীতি বিশ্বের সকলে মাঝে পৌছাবে।তবে প্রতিটা গানের নিচে ইংরেজি টাইটেল দেওয়া উচিত। 🙏🙏
